  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you hit a creature with a weapon attack, you can expend one superiority die to attempt to drive the target back. You add the superiority die to the attack's damage roll, and if the target is Large or smaller, it must make a Strength saving throw. On a failed save, you push the target up to 15 feet away from you.</p>\n<p><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813;font-size:13px\">Note: After adding this feature to your character, edit this feature's details and set Resource Consumption to Items Uses: Combat Superiority.</em></p>",
